name: Johnnie Traveler's
description: This project showcases the deployment of static websites using GitHub Pages, a free hosting service from GitHub. It allows users to turn their repositories into websites that are automatically updated with every push. The pages are built using Jekyll, Hugo, or other static site generators, and are ideal for hosting documentation, blogs, portfolios, or project landing pages.

name: Quiz App
description: A Quiz App is an interactive platform designed to test users' knowledge across a variety of subjects, such as general knowledge, science, history, and more. The app offers multiple-choice questions, timed quizzes, and real-time scoring to create an engaging learning experience. With features like customizable quiz categories, leaderboards, and performance tracking, users can challenge themselves and others. The app is user-friendly and suitable for learners of all ages, allowing for self-paced quizzes or competitive challenges. Ideal for both casual learning and serious study preparation.

name: Infrastructure
description: Infrastructure automation using Terraform and Ansible on IBM Cloud provides a powerful combination for provisioning, managing, and configuring cloud resources efficiently.
